{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"title","type":"text","x":-80,"y":-840,"width":1400,"height":90,"text":"# Zoom-in — two backbone events, expanded\nDetail for **Candidates Generated (per method)** and **Step Result Recorded** from [[Event Storming — TRIZ Solver.canvas|the backbone]]. 🟧 = event (past tense) · grey = data / external system."},
		{"id":"grpA","type":"group","x":-80,"y":-720,"width":2560,"height":560,"label":"🔍 A — Candidates Generated (per method): fan-out over methods → converge"},
