		{"id":"rec","type":"text","x":980,"y":10,"width":560,"height":210,"text":"🗄️ StepResult\n• run_version · step_id · status\n• inputs — refs to upstream outputs\n• output\n• method\n• model + params\n• tokens / cost\n• timestamp · duration"},
		{"id":"why","type":"text","x":980,"y":250,"width":560,"height":110,"text":"Why each field earns points:\nmethod+model+params → reproducibility · inputs → re-run from step · tokens/cost+duration → Day-4 eval metrics & Day-5 perf · run_version → compare iterations"},
